00:33:44,860 --> 00:33:45,700
(Fan,)

585
00:33:46,160 --> 00:33:47,980
(I will take good care of Li.)

586
00:33:48,700 --> 00:33:49,540
(Don't worry.)

587
00:33:52,010 --> 00:33:53,780
(We will remember Fan)

588
00:33:54,270 --> 00:33:56,190
(and those who have passed.)

589
00:33:57,230 --> 00:34:00,990
♪Will not be in vain♪

590
00:34:04,060 --> 00:34:05,300
Since you left,

591
00:34:06,500 --> 00:34:08,700
I've never gotten lucky
when drawing grass straws.

592
00:34:10,020 --> 00:34:11,100
Today,

593
00:34:11,220 --> 00:34:12,500
we brought good wine

594
00:34:14,140 --> 00:34:15,060
to come and see you.

595
00:34:16,980 --> 00:34:17,820
Cheers.

596
00:34:18,380 --> 00:34:20,700
(Grave of Wei Liang)

597
00:34:21,540 --> 00:34:22,740
Xiaotao came too.

598
00:34:42,020 --> 00:34:44,380
This is the orchid you brought back.

599
00:34:47,020 --> 00:34:47,940
I water it

600
00:34:48,820 --> 00:34:50,260
and give it sun

601
00:34:50,980 --> 00:34:52,380
every day.

602
00:34:53,540 --> 00:34:55,540
It's growing well now.

603
00:34:57,660 --> 00:34:59,020
You're the kind of man

604
00:34:59,380 --> 00:35:00,980
who can't keep promises.

605
00:35:02,020 --> 00:35:02,860
See?

606
00:35:04,180 --> 00:35:05,880
In the end,
I'm the one bringing the orchid

607
00:35:05,880 --> 00:35:06,740
to propose to you.

608
00:35:13,620 --> 00:35:15,740
Whether you're alive or dead,

609
00:35:17,780 --> 00:35:20,060
I still want to marry you.

610
00:35:20,860 --> 00:35:24,060
(Grave of Wei Liang)

611
00:35:31,340 --> 00:35:32,860
In our hearts,

612
00:35:33,460 --> 00:35:34,620
these little weapons

613
00:35:34,780 --> 00:35:36,100
represent us.

614
00:35:37,060 --> 00:35:39,580
We weren't born on the same day

615
00:35:40,380 --> 00:35:41,340
and probably

616
00:35:41,540 --> 00:35:43,580
won't die on the same day.

617
00:35:45,220 --> 00:35:46,100
But one day,

618
00:35:47,140 --> 00:35:48,860
if we're all gone,

619
00:35:49,500 --> 00:35:51,100
with these weapons buried together,

620
00:35:52,020 --> 00:35:53,620
we'll always be brothers.

621
00:35:56,820 --> 00:35:57,700
Seeing it

622
00:35:58,300 --> 00:35:59,740
will be like seeing me.

623
00:36:05,460 --> 00:36:06,340
Is this a sign

624
00:36:06,620 --> 00:36:07,860
to stop fighting?

625
00:36:09,920 --> 00:36:13,060
How did you manage to say that
in such a circumstance?

626
00:37:27,900 --> 00:37:28,740
Sir.

627
00:37:29,620 --> 00:37:30,700
Has the Lord been found?

628
00:37:30,900 --> 00:37:31,840
He's not at the office.

629
00:37:33,220 --> 00:37:34,060
Sir.

630
00:37:34,420 --> 00:37:35,360
Not the training ground.

631
00:37:36,900 --> 00:37:37,740
Sir.

632
00:37:38,620 --> 00:37:39,580
Lady Xu also said

633
00:37:39,580 --> 00:37:40,620
she hadn't seen the Lord.

634
00:37:41,440 --> 00:37:43,200
The deer offering ritual
is about to start.

635
00:37:43,200 --> 00:37:43,900
Without the Lord,

636
00:37:43,920 --> 00:37:45,220
how can the ritual be completed?

637
00:37:46,940 --> 00:37:48,060
Go fetch Lady Xu.

638
00:37:48,220 --> 00:37:50,300
Only she can accept the deer

639
00:37:50,300 --> 00:37:51,580
on behalf of the Lord.

640
00:37:51,740 --> 00:37:52,900
- Hurry.
- Yes.

641
00:38:00,940 --> 00:38:02,500
Don't cry.

642
00:38:04,420 --> 00:38:06,420
Stop crying.

643
00:38:08,660 --> 00:38:09,500
Don't cry.

644
00:38:13,580 --> 00:38:15,380
The ritual has started.

645
00:38:15,660 --> 00:38:16,940
Mr. Gongsun couldn't find you

646
00:38:16,940 --> 00:38:18,420
and brought Grandmother there.

647
00:38:18,700 --> 00:38:20,300
- Why are you here?
- Well.

648
00:38:20,300 --> 00:38:21,580
Feifei has been crying nonstop.

649
00:38:21,940 --> 00:38:23,780
I couldn't go.

650
00:38:25,740 --> 00:38:26,700
Alright.

651
00:38:26,900 --> 00:38:27,900
Good girl.

652
00:38:27,900 --> 00:38:29,540
Come on.

653
00:38:30,420 --> 00:38:31,260
Go to your mother.

654
00:38:32,020 --> 00:38:33,180
Don't cry.

655
00:38:35,260 --> 00:38:36,220
You're amazing.

656
00:38:43,260 --> 00:38:45,300
(Grandfather once compared
living a life)

657
00:38:45,300 --> 00:38:46,860
(to conquering the world.)

658
00:38:47,460 --> 00:38:48,700
(He said)

659
00:38:48,700 --> 00:38:50,740
(both required equal strength.)

660
00:38:51,260 --> 00:38:52,100
(Now,)

661
00:38:52,300 --> 00:38:53,460
(I think those words)

662
00:38:54,100 --> 00:38:55,740
(can be understood another way.)

663
00:38:56,860 --> 00:38:58,500
(Whether it's to live a life)

664
00:38:58,700 --> 00:39:00,060
(or conquer the world,)

665
00:39:00,780 --> 00:39:02,940
(both sides working together)

666
00:39:03,100 --> 00:39:04,900
(is the way to last.)

667
00:39:06,220 --> 00:39:08,100
(Luckily, my husband and I)

668
00:39:08,380 --> 00:39:09,980
(still understand)

669
00:39:10,340 --> 00:39:11,740
(and are devoted to each other)

670
00:39:11,900 --> 00:39:13,180
(after weathering many storms.)

671
00:39:14,540 --> 00:39:16,180
(He's willing to become my prisoner,)

672
00:39:17,100 --> 00:39:19,140
(and I'm willing to be his.)

673
00:39:33,220 --> 00:39:38,620
(Wei Mansion)

674
00:39:41,020 --> 00:39:42,140
(Years later,)

675
00:39:42,160 --> 00:39:43,920
(the Yongning Canal
brought huge benefits.)

676
00:39:44,260 --> 00:39:45,580
(The waterways are connected,)

677
00:39:45,580 --> 00:39:46,820
(benefiting all sides.)

678
00:39:47,380 --> 00:39:49,500
(The world is thus freed
from strife and hatred.)

679
00:39:49,940 --> 00:39:51,820
(The people are at peace.)

680
00:39:53,420 --> 00:39:55,260
(I've finally had
my lifelong wish come true)

681
00:39:55,860 --> 00:39:57,140
(by traveling with my wife)

682
00:39:57,420 --> 00:39:58,780
(to see the world.)

683
00:40:00,370 --> 00:40:03,130
(Thanks to the companions
on this journey.)

684
00:40:03,130 --> 00:40:04,520
(Everyone,)

685
00:40:04,520 --> 00:40:05,880
(in the years to come,)

686
00:40:06,260 --> 00:40:07,730
(may all your wishes come true.)

687
00:40:11,980 --> 00:40:15,180
(The end)

688
00:40:34,390 --> 00:40:37,220
♪The moonlight is as silent
as the deep sea♪

689
00:40:38,290 --> 00:40:40,750
♪From afar♪

690
00:40:42,700 --> 00:40:45,850
♪It once lit up dreams with a breath♪

691
00:40:46,770 --> 00:40:49,880
♪But vanished with a sigh♪

692
00:40:51,100 --> 00:40:54,470
♪Brushing past my fingertips♪

693
00:40:54,870 --> 00:40:58,240
♪My heartstrings were stirred quietly♪

694
00:40:59,070 --> 00:41:01,010
♪As if we once met before♪

695
00:41:01,500 --> 00:41:05,610
♪Holding back a love so deep♪

696
00:41:07,900 --> 00:41:11,270
♪Love asks for nothing in the end♪

697
00:41:11,860 --> 00:41:14,940
♪Leaving only obsessions♪

698
00:41:16,260 --> 00:41:19,660
♪I've wandered in the world♪

699
00:41:20,160 --> 00:41:23,160
♪Yet cannot have it all♪

700
00:41:24,720 --> 00:41:27,990
♪We meet and part in the fires of war♪

701
00:41:28,310 --> 00:41:32,000
♪Embracing,
leaving tender marks of love♪

702
00:41:32,700 --> 00:41:34,630
♪With one breathtaking glance♪

703
00:41:35,170 --> 00:41:40,090
♪How could I ever forget♪

704
00:41:40,670 --> 00:41:42,950
♪I would cross mountains and seas♪

705
00:41:42,950 --> 00:41:45,470
♪To spend time with you♪

706
00:41:45,720 --> 00:41:47,080
♪When we grow old♪

707
00:41:47,080 --> 00:41:49,670
♪Nothing will change♪

708
00:41:49,670 --> 00:41:51,270
♪The misty rains never cease♪

709
00:41:51,270 --> 00:41:54,130
♪Falling gently on your brow♪

710
00:41:54,130 --> 00:41:58,120
♪Lingering in my heart♪

711
00:41:58,120 --> 00:41:59,820
♪I would sever fate's ties♪

712
00:41:59,820 --> 00:42:02,240
♪To protect your smiling eyes♪

713
00:42:02,630 --> 00:42:06,500
♪Even if behind me lies a storm♪

